      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and is ready for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, with only the expected minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. All body panels are straight with factory-consistent gaps. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and well-preserved; the leather bolsters show minimal wear, and all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It comes with a complete service history showing oil changes every 5,000 miles. Within the last year, we have replaced the battery, installed a fresh set of all-season tires with 80% tread remaining, and performed a full brake service. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts crisply, and there are no warning lights on the dashboard. This is a reliable, attractive daily driver that balances performance with comfort. Includes two sets of keys and the original owner\u2019s manuals.",
